      "rdfs:comment": "Prism-level constraint vocabulary. Each constraint is a type:Constraint subclass whose fiber-pinning behavior derives from foundation components.",
      "prism:space": "user",
      "owl:imports": [
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/partition/"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/type/",
      "@type": "owl:Ontology",
      "rdfs:label": "Prism Types",
      "rdfs:comment": "Prism-level type definitions. Each type is an algebraic composition of foundation types parameterized for the Prism runtime.",
      "prism:space": "user",
      "owl:imports": [
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/morphism/"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/constraint/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "ComposedOperation",
      "rdfs:comment": "An operation formed by composing two or more foundation operations. The composition is witnessed by a morphism:CompositionLaw and each component is a foundation op:Operation.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Operation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "InferenceOperation",
      "rdfs:comment": "The composed inference operation ι = P∘Π∘G: surface symbol → GroundingMap → resolution pipeline → ProjectionMap → surface symbol. Typed by the Surface Symmetry Theorem (op:surfaceSymmetry). Idempotent on SaturatedContext (SC_5). The atomic unit of Prism computation.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "AccumulationOperation",
      "rdfs:comment": "The accumulation operator α: Binding × Context → Context. Appends a resolved binding to the session accumulator, monotonically reducing freeCount (SR_1). Associative: binding order does not affect the final saturated state (SR_10 confluence). The empty context is the identity element (SR_2).",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "LeasePartitionOperation",
      "rdfs:comment": "The lease partition operator λ: Context × ℕ → ContextLease^k. Splits a SharedContext into k disjoint ContextLease instances. Conserves total budget (MC_1). Produces disjoint leases (SR_9). Composition of all leased results recovers the original saturation (MC_6).",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "DispatchOperation",
      "rdfs:comment": "The dispatch operator δ: Query × ResolverRegistry → Resolver. Selects the concrete resolver for a given query. Deterministic, type-respecting, and monotone in specificity.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "SessionCompositionOperation",
      "rdfs:comment": "The composition operator κ: Session × Session → Session. Merges binding sets of completed sessions via state:SessionComposition. Valid iff SR_8 tower consistency holds. Full lease coverage implies composed saturation σ=1 (MC_6). Resolved results compose in O(1) (MC_7). Per-session work bounded at ⌈n/k⌉ (MC_8).",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismVerificationDomain",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "PrismVerificationDomain",
      "rdfs:comment": "Verification domain for Prism-layer identities. Extends the foundation VerificationDomain vocabulary with Prism-specific algebraic domains.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/VerificationDomain"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverRegistry",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "ResolverRegistry",
      "rdfs:comment": "The dispatch table mapping query types to resolver types. Consumed by the DispatchOperation. Immutable after deployment.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverBinding"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverBinding",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "ResolverBinding",
      "rdfs:comment": "A single entry in the ResolverRegistry: maps a foundation query:Query subclass to a foundation resolver:Resolver subclass with a priority and dispatch predicate.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverRegistry"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/BaseContext",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "BaseContext",
      "rdfs:comment": "A pre-populated Context serving as the initial state for an accumulation sequence. A BaseContext has σ > 0: it carries existing bindings (an OS userland, a pre-trained model, a bootstrapped database) before any Prism session begins. Accumulation via α extends the base without overwriting existing bindings (PA_4). Domain-agnostic: a filesystem image and a neural network checkpoint are structurally identical BaseContext instances.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/Context"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/cascade/TargetConvergenceAngle",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "TargetConvergenceAngle",
      "rdfs:comment": "The pipeline's target is convergence at the Euler Identity e^(iπ) = −1 (180°). The system executes recursive phase rotations (each applying Ω = e^(iπ/6)) until the state vector reaches −1. Convergence is mathematically determined: the target angle is always 180°, and the pipeline either converges or produces a typed failure witness at the specific phase gate where attestation failed. Expressed as a ConstrainedType whose constraint nerve defines the fibers that must be pinned for the full 180° rotation to complete.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/ConstrainedType"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/type/InferenceType"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/type/SessionType"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/type/LeaseType"
        }
      ],
      "cascade:targetAngle": 180,
      "cascade:convergenceValue": "-1"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/baseImage",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "baseImage",
      "rdfs:comment": "The content-addressed identifier of the base snapshot. Links a BaseContext to its canonical address in the ring, enabling verification that the base state matches its declared content hash.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/BaseContext"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/u/Address"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/baseSaturation",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "baseSaturation",
      "rdfs:comment": "The saturation degree σ of the BaseContext at initialization. 0 < baseSaturation ≤ 1. A BaseContext with baseSaturation = 1 is already fully saturated (a SaturatedContext).",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/BaseContext"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/baseFiberMask",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "baseFiberMask",
      "rdfs:comment": "The FiberBudget of the BaseContext at initialization: which fibers are already pinned by the base snapshot. Subsequent accumulation can only pin free fibers (PA_4).",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/BaseContext"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/partition/FiberBudget"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/desiredConstraint",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "desiredConstraint",
      "rdfs:comment": "A constraint that must be satisfied for the pipeline to converge at the target angle (180°). Non-functional: multiple constraints define the fiber pinning required for full phase rotation. The runtime resolves the difference between baseContext's pinned fibers and the convergence constraints.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/cascade/TargetConvergenceAngle"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/Constraint"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/targetContext",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "targetContext",
      "rdfs:comment": "The BaseContext against which the TargetConvergenceAngle is evaluated. The runtime computes the fiber deficit between this context and the convergence constraints.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/cascade/TargetConvergenceAngle"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/BaseContext"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityResult",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "FeasibilityResult",
      "rdfs:comment": "The abstract result of a feasibility assessment on a TargetConvergenceAngle. Exactly one of its two disjoint subclasses: FeasibilityWitness (the target is achievable) or InfeasibilityWitness (the target is unrealizable). Serves as the typed union for the feasibilityResult property.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointUnionOf": {
        "@list": [
          {
            "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityWitness"
          },
          {
            "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityWitness"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityWitness",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "FeasibilityWitness",
      "rdfs:comment": "Evidence that a TargetConvergenceAngle is achievable from its targetContext. Carries the constraint sufficiency check (CB_5) result and the estimated iteration bound (CB_6). Produced by the runtime before pipeline execution begins. Absence of a FeasibilityWitness means feasibility has not been assessed — not that the target is infeasible.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityResult"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityWitness"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityWitness",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "InfeasibilityWitness",
      "rdfs:comment": "Evidence that a TargetConvergenceAngle cannot be reached from its targetContext. Two sub-cases: insufficiency (the constraint set does not cover all required fibers — CB_5 fails) and contradiction (two constraints pin the same fiber to different values — SR_5). Links to the specific constraints or fibers causing infeasibility.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityResult"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityWitness"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityKind",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "InfeasibilityKind",
      "rdfs:comment": "A typed controlled vocabulary for infeasibility reasons: Insufficient (constraint set does not cover the target fibers) or Contradictory (constraints conflict on the same fiber). Follows the foundation's SessionBoundaryType pattern.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/Insufficient",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityKind"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "Insufficient",
      "rdfs:comment": "The TargetConvergenceAngle's constraint set does not pin all required fibers. CB_5 (sufficiency criterion) fails: ∪_i pins(C_i) ⊊ {0,...,n−1}. Resolution would stall at PartialSaturation."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/Contradictory",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityKind"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "Contradictory",
      "rdfs:comment": "Two or more constraints in the TargetConvergenceAngle pin the same fiber to different values. SR_5 (ContradictionBoundary) would fire during accumulation. The target is unrealizable regardless of constraint sufficiency."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/feasibilityResult",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "feasibilityResult",
      "rdfs:comment": "The feasibility or infeasibility witness for this TargetConvergenceAngle. Exactly one of FeasibilityWitness or InfeasibilityWitness. Absent means feasibility has not been assessed.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/cascade/TargetConvergenceAngle"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityResult"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/estimatedIterations",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "estimatedIterations",
      "rdfs:comment": "Upper bound on iterations to reach saturation from the targetContext, derived from CB_6: ≤ min(k, n) for k constraints. Present only on FeasibilityWitness.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityWitness"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/coveredFibers",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "coveredFibers",
      "rdfs:comment": "The number of fibers the constraint set can pin. If coveredFibers < totalFibers, the infeasibility kind is Insufficient.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FeasibilityWitness"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/infeasibilityKind",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "infeasibilityKind",
      "rdfs:comment": "The typed reason for infeasibility: Insufficient or Contradictory.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityWitness"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityKind"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/conflictingConstraints",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "conflictingConstraints",
      "rdfs:comment": "The constraints that conflict on a specific fiber, causing infeasibility. Non-functional: two or more constraints may be involved. Present only when infeasibilityKind = Contradictory.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityWitness"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/Constraint"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/uncoveredFiber",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "uncoveredFiber",
      "rdfs:comment": "A FiberCoordinate that no constraint in the TargetConvergenceAngle can pin. Non-functional: multiple fibers may be uncovered. Present only when infeasibilityKind = Insufficient.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InfeasibilityWitness"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/partition/FiberCoordinate"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/synthesisGoal",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "synthesisGoal",
      "rdfs:comment": "When a TargetConvergenceAngle's constraint set is insufficient but the topological target is known, the runtime promotes the TargetConvergenceAngle to a TypeSynthesisGoal for the foundation's ψ-pipeline inversion (Amendment 28). The TypeSynthesisResolver searches for additional constraints that would close the fiber budget. Absent when the TargetConvergenceAngle is already sufficient (CB_5 passes).",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/cascade/TargetConvergenceAngle"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/TypeSynthesisGoal"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/synthesizedBasis",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "synthesizedBasis",
      "rdfs:comment": "The MinimalConstraintBasis produced by the TypeSynthesisResolver for this TargetConvergenceAngle. The minimal set of constraints sufficient to close the fiber budget. Present only when synthesis succeeds. The synthesized constraints are fed back into the TargetConvergenceAngle's constraint set for execution.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/cascade/TargetConvergenceAngle"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/MinimalConstraintBasis"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismInstance",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "PrismInstance",
      "rdfs:comment": "The root deployment object binding a BaseContext, a ResolverRegistry, and a TargetConvergenceAngle into a single execution configuration. Immutable after construction. The Prism analog of the foundation's schema:Ring — the single object that fully determines the system's behavior. Under the Euler Cascade, the system executes recursive phase rotations until each target converges at e^(iπ) = −1.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineState",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "PipelineState",
      "rdfs:comment": "The current execution state of a query flowing through the Euler Cascade pipeline. Tracks which PipelineStage is active (parameterized by E(k) = Ω^k), the fiber budget at each phase transition, the complex-valued state vector, and the accumulated PipelineTrace. Advances deterministically through six 30° phase rotations: Initialization (0°) → Declare (30°) → Factorize (60°) → Resolve (90°) → Attest (120°) → Extract (150°) → Convergence (180°), or Failed at any stage. The state vector must equal Ω^k at stage k for the state to be valid (Phase Gate Attestation).",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineStage",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "PipelineStage",
      "rdfs:comment": "A typed controlled vocabulary for Euler Cascade pipeline stages. Each named individual corresponds to a position E(k) = Ω^k in the cascade function, where Ω = e^(iπ/6). Eight stages: Initialization (E(0) = 1, 0°), Declare (E(1) = Ω, 30°), Factorize (E(2) = Ω², 60°), Resolve (E(3) = i, 90°), Attest (E(4) = Ω⁴, 120°), Extract (E(5) = Ω⁵, 150°), Convergence (E(6) = e^(iπ) = −1, 180°), Failed (terminal, no phase). Pipeline states are geometrically determined by their phase angle rather than assigned by arbitrary sequential indexing.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "DomainPackage",
      "rdfs:comment": "A bundled domain adapter pairing a GroundingMap and ProjectionMap for a specific surface representation. Tells the Prism pipeline how to ground symbols from a specific domain (text, grid, audio, filesystem, model weights) and how to project resolved partitions back. Domain-agnostic at the algebraic level (PA_5), domain-specific at the surface level.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/instanceBase",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "instanceBase",
      "rdfs:comment": "The BaseContext serving as the initial state for this Prism deployment.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismInstance"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/BaseContext"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/instanceRegistry",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "instanceRegistry",
      "rdfs:comment": "The ResolverRegistry providing dispatch bindings for this Prism deployment.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismInstance"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverRegistry"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/instanceTarget",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "instanceTarget",
      "rdfs:comment": "A TargetConvergenceAngle specification for this deployment. Non-functional: a PrismInstance may target multiple convergence angles (e.g., both an OS image target and a model weight target in a unified supply chain deployment). Each target converges independently at e^(iπ) = −1.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismInstance"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/cascade/TargetConvergenceAngle"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/instanceDomain",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "instanceDomain",
      "rdfs:comment": "A DomainPackage registered with this Prism deployment. Non-functional: a PrismInstance may handle multiple domains (e.g., text + grid + filesystem in the same deployment).",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismInstance"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/instanceQuantumLevel",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "instanceQuantumLevel",
      "rdfs:comment": "The quantum level at which this Prism instance operates. Determines the ring size and register width.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismInstance"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#positiveInteger"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/currentStage",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "currentStage",
      "rdfs:comment": "The PipelineStage currently active in this PipelineState.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineState"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineStage"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/pipelineBudget",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "pipelineBudget",
      "rdfs:comment": "The FiberBudget snapshot at the current pipeline stage. Updated at each stage transition.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineState"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/partition/FiberBudget"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/pipelineInstance",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "pipelineInstance",
      "rdfs:comment": "The PrismInstance this pipeline execution belongs to.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineState"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismInstance"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/packageGrounding",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "packageGrounding",
      "rdfs:comment": "The GroundingMap implementation provided by this DomainPackage.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/morphism/GroundingMap"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/packageProjection",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "packageProjection",
      "rdfs:comment": "The ProjectionMap implementation provided by this DomainPackage.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/morphism/ProjectionMap"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/packageVocabularyType",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "packageVocabularyType",
      "rdfs:comment": "The TypeDefinition of the surface symbol space handled by this DomainPackage.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/TypeDefinition"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/sharedFrameAsserted",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "sharedFrameAsserted",
      "rdfs:comment": "The state:Frame shared between this DomainPackage's GroundingMap and ProjectionMap. The Surface Symmetry Theorem (PI_2) requires frame(G) = frame(P) for well-typedness. This property makes the shared-frame condition explicit at the package level rather than implicit in the identities.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/Frame"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/packageCoherent",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "packageCoherent",
      "rdfs:comment": "Whether this DomainPackage has been validated for round-trip coherence: P(Π(G(s))) lands in the type-equivalent neighbourhood of s for all s in the vocabulary type. True iff the shared-frame condition holds and the grounding/projection pair satisfies PI_5. A package with packageCoherent = false is structurally invalid and must not be used for inference.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/packageCertificate",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "packageCertificate",
      "rdfs:comment": "The GroundingCertificate attesting round-trip coherence for this DomainPackage. Issued when packageCoherent = true. Links to the foundation's morphism:GroundingCertificate which witnesses the Surface Symmetry Theorem for the package's grounding/projection pair.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DomainPackage"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/morphism/GroundingCertificate"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/composedFrom",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "composedFrom",
      "rdfs:comment": "A foundation entity that is a component of this composed Prism operation. Non-functional: a ComposedOperation may have two or more components spanning Operations, Transforms, and Resolvers. Range is intentionally owl:Thing because OWL 2 DL does not support union ranges and the components cross foundation class hierarchies. Type narrowing is handled by the typed component properties on each operator subclass (groundingComponent, resolutionComponent, projectionComponent, etc.).",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/compositionWitness",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "compositionWitness",
      "rdfs:comment": "The morphism:CompositionLaw witnessing the composition that defines this operation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/morphism/CompositionLaw"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/groundingComponent",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "groundingComponent",
      "rdfs:comment": "The GroundingMap component G of an InferenceOperation ι = P∘Π∘G.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/morphism/GroundingMap"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/resolutionComponent",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "resolutionComponent",
      "rdfs:comment": "The resolution pipeline component Π of an InferenceOperation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/resolver/Resolver"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/projectionComponent",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "projectionComponent",
      "rdfs:comment": "The ProjectionMap component P of an InferenceOperation ι = P∘Π∘G.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/morphism/ProjectionMap"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/leaseCount",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "leaseCount",
      "rdfs:comment": "The number of disjoint leases k produced by a LeasePartitionOperation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#positiveInteger"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/partitionedContext",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "partitionedContext",
      "rdfs:comment": "The SharedContext being partitioned by a LeasePartitionOperation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/SharedContext"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/hasBinding",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "hasBinding",
      "rdfs:comment": "A ResolverBinding entry in this ResolverRegistry. Non-functional: a registry contains multiple bindings.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverRegistry"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverBinding"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/boundQueryType",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "boundQueryType",
      "rdfs:comment": "The foundation query:Query subclass this binding dispatches.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverBinding"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/boundResolverType",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "boundResolverType",
      "rdfs:comment": "The foundation resolver:Resolver subclass this binding routes to.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverBinding"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/bindingPriority",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "bindingPriority",
      "rdfs:comment": "Dispatch priority for this binding. Lower values take precedence.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverBinding"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchPredicate",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "DispatchPredicate",
      "rdfs:comment": "A typed predicate evaluated by the dispatch operator δ to narrow a ResolverBinding match beyond query type. Subclasses type:Constraint but specialized for dispatch-time evaluation: the predicate reads the query's relationType and the session context's saturation state to decide whether this binding applies. A ResolverBinding with no dispatchPredicate matches all queries of its declared type.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://uor.foundation/type/Constraint"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/constraint/LatencyConstraint"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/constraint/ThroughputConstraint"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/constraint/CoherenceConstraint"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/gate/PhaseGateAttestation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SaturationPredicate",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "SaturationPredicate",
      "rdfs:comment": "A dispatch predicate that matches when the session context's saturation degree σ ≥ minSaturation. Used to route queries to different resolvers based on how much of the fiber budget is already closed.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchPredicate"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FiberCoveragePredicate"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/QuerySubtypePredicate"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FiberCoveragePredicate",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "FiberCoveragePredicate",
      "rdfs:comment": "A dispatch predicate that matches when specific fibers are already pinned in the session context. Used to route queries that depend on prior resolution of specific fiber positions.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchPredicate"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SaturationPredicate"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/QuerySubtypePredicate"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/QuerySubtypePredicate",
      "@type": "owl:Class",
      "rdfs:label": "QuerySubtypePredicate",
      "rdfs:comment": "A dispatch predicate that matches when the incoming query is an instance of a specific query:Query subclass. Used for fine-grained routing beyond the boundQueryType on the ResolverBinding.",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchPredicate"
        }
      ],
      "owl:disjointWith": [
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SaturationPredicate"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FiberCoveragePredicate"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/minSaturation",
      "@type": [
        "owl:DatatypeProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "minSaturation",
      "rdfs:comment": "The minimum σ required for this predicate to match. Range [0, 1].",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SaturationPredicate"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/requiredFibers",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "requiredFibers",
      "rdfs:comment": "A FiberCoordinate that must be pinned for this predicate to match. Non-functional: multiple fibers may be required.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/FiberCoveragePredicate"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/partition/FiberCoordinate"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/requiredQueryType",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "requiredQueryType",
      "rdfs:comment": "The specific query:Query subclass the incoming query must be an instance of for this predicate to match.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/QuerySubtypePredicate"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/dispatchPredicate",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "dispatchPredicate",
      "rdfs:comment": "A typed dispatch predicate that must be satisfied for this binding to match an incoming query. Evaluated by δ before routing. If absent, the binding matches all queries of the declared boundQueryType. When present, narrows the match to queries whose relationType satisfies this predicate.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverBinding"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchPredicate"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/inputSymbol",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "inputSymbol",
      "rdfs:comment": "The surface symbol entering the inference operation ι = P∘Π∘G.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/schema/Literal"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/inferenceContext",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "inferenceContext",
      "rdfs:comment": "The session context against which the inference operation resolves.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/Context"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/outputSymbol",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "outputSymbol",
      "rdfs:comment": "The surface symbol produced by the inference operation after projection.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/schema/Literal"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/accumulatedBinding",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "accumulatedBinding",
      "rdfs:comment": "The binding being appended by an AccumulationOperation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/Binding"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/inputContext",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "inputContext",
      "rdfs:comment": "The context before the accumulation operation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/Context"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/outputContext",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "outputContext",
      "rdfs:comment": "The context after the accumulation operation. freeCount(outputContext) ≤ freeCount(inputContext) by SR_1.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/Context"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/dispatchedQuery",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "dispatchedQuery",
      "rdfs:comment": "The query submitted to the dispatch operator for resolver selection.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/query/Query"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/usesRegistry",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "usesRegistry",
      "rdfs:comment": "The ResolverRegistry consulted by this dispatch operation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ResolverRegistry"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/selectedResolver",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "selectedResolver",
      "rdfs:comment": "The resolver selected by the dispatch operation. inputType(selectedResolver) ⊇ declaredType(query) by PD_2.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/resolver/Resolver"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/composedSession",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "composedSession",
      "rdfs:comment": "An input session being merged by a SessionCompositionOperation. Non-functional: two or more sessions may be composed.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/Session"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/compositionResult",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "compositionResult",
      "rdfs:comment": "The SessionComposition result of a valid composition. Present only when SR_8 tower consistency holds.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/SessionComposition"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/producedLease",
      "@type": "owl:ObjectProperty",
      "rdfs:label": "producedLease",
      "rdfs:comment": "A ContextLease produced by a LeasePartitionOperation. Non-functional: k leases are produced.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/state/ContextLease"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/hasComplexity",
      "@type": [
        "owl:ObjectProperty",
        "owl:FunctionalProperty"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "hasComplexity",
      "rdfs:comment": "The computational complexity class of this Prism operation.",
      "rdfs:domain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/ComposedOperation"
      },
      "rdfs:range": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/resolver/ComplexityClass"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceAlgebraic",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismVerificationDomain"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "InferenceAlgebraic",
      "rdfs:comment": "Verification domain for identities governing the inference operation ι = P∘Π∘G."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationAlgebraic",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismVerificationDomain"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "AccumulationAlgebraic",
      "rdfs:comment": "Verification domain for identities governing the accumulation operator α."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeaseAlgebraic",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismVerificationDomain"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "LeaseAlgebraic",
      "rdfs:comment": "Verification domain for identities governing the lease partition operator λ."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchAlgebraic",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismVerificationDomain"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "DispatchAlgebraic",
      "rdfs:comment": "Verification domain for identities governing the dispatch operator δ."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/CompositionAlgebraic",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismVerificationDomain"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "CompositionAlgebraic",
      "rdfs:comment": "Verification domain for identities governing the session composition operator κ."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineAlgebraic",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PrismVerificationDomain"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PipelineAlgebraic",
      "rdfs:comment": "Verification domain for the pipeline unification identity PP_1: the equation unifying the six Euler Cascade operators into a single resolution equivalent to the product of six 30° phase rotations converging at e^(iπ) = −1."
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/infer",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceOperation"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "infer",
      "rdfs:comment": "The named inference operation ι = P∘Π∘G. Arity 2 (symbol × context). Not commutative, not associative. Idempotent on SaturatedContext (PI_1). Complexity: O(n) worst case, O(1) on CompleteType.",
      "op:arity": 2,
      "op:commutative": false,
      "op:associative": false
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/accumulate",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationOperation"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "accumulate",
      "rdfs:comment": "The named accumulation operator α: Binding × Context → Context. Arity 2. Not commutative (binding and context are different types). Associative at convergence (PA_1 via SR_10). Complexity: O(1).",
      "op:arity": 2,
      "op:commutative": false,
      "op:associative": true
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/partition",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeasePartitionOperation"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "partition",
      "rdfs:comment": "The named lease partition operator λ: SharedContext × ℕ → ContextLease^k. Arity 2 (context × lease count). Not commutative, not associative. Complexity: O(k).",
      "op:arity": 2,
      "op:commutative": false,
      "op:associative": false
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/dispatch",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchOperation"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "dispatch",
      "rdfs:comment": "The named dispatch operator δ: Query × ResolverRegistry → Resolver. Arity 2. Not commutative, not associative. Deterministic (PD_1). Complexity: O(log k) for k bindings.",
      "op:arity": 2,
      "op:commutative": false,
      "op:associative": false
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/compose",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/SessionCompositionOperation"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "compose",
      "rdfs:comment": "The named session composition operator κ: Session × Session → Session. Arity 2. Commutative under disjoint leases (MC_4). Associative (SR_8 tower consistency is transitive). Complexity: O(n).",
      "op:arity": 2,
      "op:commutative": true,
      "op:associative": true
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PI_1",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PI_1",
      "rdfs:comment": "Inference idempotence on saturated contexts: ι(ι(s, C_sat), C_sat) = ι(s, C_sat). A fully saturated context absorbs repeated inference.",
      "op:lhs": "ι(ι(s, C_sat), C_sat)",
      "op:rhs": "ι(s, C_sat)",
      "op:forAll": "s: Literal, C_sat: SaturatedContext",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "CC_1 (CompleteType → O(1)) + SC_5 (SaturatedContext → O(1) subsequent) → idempotence"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PI_2",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PI_2",
      "rdfs:comment": "Inference well-typedness under shared-frame: ι(s, C) is well-typed iff the GroundingMap and ProjectionMap share the same state:Frame.",
      "op:lhs": "ι(s, C) well-typed",
      "op:rhs": "frame(G) = frame(P)",
      "op:forAll": "s: Literal, C: Context, G: GroundingMap, P: ProjectionMap",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "op:surfaceSymmetry → shared-frame condition → well-typedness"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PI_3",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PI_3",
      "rdfs:comment": "Inference monotonicity: freeCount(C') ≤ freeCount(C) after ι(s, C) → C'. Each inference step either pins fibers or is a no-op.",
      "op:lhs": "freeCount(ι(s, C).context)",
      "op:rhs": "≤ freeCount(C)",
      "op:forAll": "s: Literal, C: Context",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "SR_1 (binding monotonicity) → inference monotonicity via α composition"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PI_4",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PI_4",
      "rdfs:comment": "Inference embedding commutativity: ι commutes with quantum level embedding. glyph(ι_k(addresses(a))) = ι_addr(a) for embedding ι: R_n → R_{n'}.",
      "op:lhs": "embed(ι_n(s, C))",
      "op:rhs": "ι_{n'}(s, embed(C))",
      "op:forAll": "s: Literal, C: Context at Q_n, embed: Embedding Q_n → Q_{n'}",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "AD_2 (addressing commutes through embeddings) + QL_ universality"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PI_5",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PI_5",
      "rdfs:comment": "Inference round-trip coherence: P(Π(G(s))) lands in the type-equivalent neighbourhood of s when the shared-frame condition holds. The operational form of GC_1.",
      "op:lhs": "type(ι(s, C))",
      "op:rhs": "≡ type(s) under frame(G).constraint",
      "op:forAll": "s: Literal, C: Context, ι well-typed (PI_2)",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/InferenceAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "GC_1 (GroundingCertificate issuance) + op:surfaceSymmetry"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PA_1",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PA_1",
      "rdfs:comment": "Accumulation associativity: α(b_3, α(b_2, α(b_1, C))) produces the same final state regardless of binding application order, on saturated convergence.",
      "op:lhs": "α(b_σ(1), α(b_σ(2), ..., α(b_σ(k), C)...))",
      "op:rhs": "= α(b_1, α(b_2, ..., α(b_k, C)...)) at convergence",
      "op:forAll": "b_1..b_k: Binding, C: Context, σ: permutation",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "SR_10 (ExecutionPolicy confluence) → permutation invariance at convergence"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PA_2",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PA_2",
      "rdfs:comment": "Accumulation identity: α(·, C_empty) = C_empty for the empty binding. The empty context with freeCount = n is the identity element.",
      "op:lhs": "α(∅, C)",
      "op:rhs": "C",
      "op:forAll": "C: Context",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "SR_2 (empty session is identity) → accumulation identity"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PA_3",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PA_3",
      "rdfs:comment": "Accumulation saturation bound: repeated application of α converges in at most n steps to σ=1 when the constraint set is sufficient (CB_5).",
      "op:lhs": "iterations to σ=1",
      "op:rhs": "≤ n (total fibers)",
      "op:forAll": "C: Context with sufficient constraints (CB_5)",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "CB_1 (min 1 fiber/iteration) + CB_5 (sufficiency) → bounded convergence"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PA_4",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PA_4",
      "rdfs:comment": "Base binding preservation: α(b, BaseContext(C_base)) preserves all bindings in C_base. Accumulation extends the base without overwriting existing pinned fibers. The Prism analog of OCI layer immutability — lower layers are never modified by upper layer application.",
      "op:lhs": "bindings(α(b, C_base)) ∩ bindings(C_base)",
      "op:rhs": "= bindings(C_base)",
      "op:forAll": "b: Binding, C_base: BaseContext",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "SR_1 (monotonicity: freeCount never increases) + fiber pinning is irreversible → base bindings preserved"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PA_5",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PA_5",
      "rdfs:comment": "Domain agnosticism: α operates identically on any Context regardless of the domain of its bindings. A filesystem binding (file at content address) and a model binding (weight tensor at content address) are algebraically indistinguishable at the ring level. The ring ℤ/(2ⁿ)ℤ does not discriminate by domain — a byte is a byte, an address is an address.",
      "op:lhs": "α(b_fs, C) algebraic structure",
      "op:rhs": "= α(b_model, C) algebraic structure (when content-address equivalent)",
      "op:forAll": "b_fs: Binding (filesystem), b_model: Binding (model), C: Context, addresses(b_fs) = addresses(b_model)",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/AccumulationAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "AD_1 (addressing bijection) + content-addressing domain independence → α is domain-blind"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PL_1",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PL_1",
      "rdfs:comment": "Lease conservation: Σ_i freeCount(λ(C, k)_i) = freeCount(C). The partition operator preserves total fiber budget.",
      "op:lhs": "Σ_i freeCount(λ(C, k)_i)",
      "op:rhs": "freeCount(C)",
      "op:forAll": "C: SharedContext, k: ℕ",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeaseAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "MC_1 (lease partition conserves budget) → direct"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PL_2",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PL_2",
      "rdfs:comment": "Lease disjointness: λ(C, k)_i ∩ λ(C, k)_j = ∅ for i ≠ j. No two leases share fiber coordinates.",
      "op:lhs": "leasedFibers(λ(C, k)_i) ∩ leasedFibers(λ(C, k)_j)",
      "op:rhs": "∅ for i ≠ j",
      "op:forAll": "C: SharedContext, k: ℕ, 1 ≤ i < j ≤ k",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeaseAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "SR_9 (ContextLease disjointness) → direct"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PL_3",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PL_3",
      "rdfs:comment": "Lease completeness recovery: κ(λ(C, k)_1, ..., λ(C, k)_k) yields σ=1 when each lease sub-session saturates its sub-domain.",
      "op:lhs": "σ(κ(S_1, ..., S_k))",
      "op:rhs": "1 when each S_i saturates its leased sub-domain",
      "op:forAll": "C: SharedContext, k leases, S_i: Session on lease i",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/LeaseAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "MC_6 (full lease coverage → composed saturation)"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PD_1",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PD_1",
      "rdfs:comment": "Dispatch determinism: δ(q, R) = δ(q, R) for all invocations. Same query and registry always yields the same resolver.",
      "op:lhs": "δ(q, R)",
      "op:rhs": "= δ(q, R) (deterministic)",
      "op:forAll": "q: Query, R: ResolverRegistry",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "ResolverRegistry immutability + priority ordering → deterministic selection"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PD_2",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PD_2",
      "rdfs:comment": "Dispatch type safety: the resolver selected by δ(q, R) accepts the query's declared type. inputType(δ(q, R)) ⊇ declaredType(q).",
      "op:lhs": "inputType(δ(q, R))",
      "op:rhs": "⊇ declaredType(q)",
      "op:forAll": "q: Query, R: ResolverRegistry, δ(q, R) defined",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/DispatchAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "ResolverBinding type constraint + OWL subclass checking"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PK_1",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PK_1",
      "rdfs:comment": "Composition validity: κ(S_A, S_B) is valid iff all pinned-fiber intersections agree at every tower level Q_0 through Q_k.",
      "op:lhs": "κ(S_A, S_B) valid",
      "op:rhs": "∀ 0 ≤ j ≤ k: bindings(S_A) ∩ bindings(S_B) agree at Q_j",
      "op:forAll": "S_A, S_B: Session at Q_k",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/CompositionAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "SR_8 (session composition tower consistency) → direct"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PK_2",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PK_2",
      "rdfs:comment": "Composition O(1) resolution: stepCount = 0 on a fully saturated composed context.",
      "op:lhs": "stepCount(resolve(q, κ(S_A, S_B).context))",
      "op:rhs": "0 when σ(κ(S_A, S_B).context) = 1",
      "op:forAll": "S_A, S_B: Session, q: Query, κ valid (PK_1)",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/CompositionAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "MC_7 (distributed O(1) resolution) → direct"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PK_3",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PK_3",
      "rdfs:comment": "Composition parallelism bound: per-session work ≤ ⌈n/k⌉ for k uniform-partition leases.",
      "op:lhs": "work(S_i) for uniform lease partition",
      "op:rhs": "≤ ⌈n/k⌉ pin operations",
      "op:forAll": "k uniform-partition leases on SharedContext with n fibers",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/CompositionAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "MC_8 (parallelism bound) → direct"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PP_1",
      "@type": [
        "owl:NamedIndividual",
        "https://uor.foundation/op/Identity"
      ],
      "rdfs:label": "PP_1",
      "rdfs:comment": "Pipeline unification: κ(λ_k(α*(ι(s, ·))), C_shared) = resolve(s, C_shared). The six Euler Cascade operators (Initialization → Declare → Factorize → Resolve → Attest → Extract → Convergence) compose into a single resolution equivalent to the product of six 30° phase rotations: E(6) = Ω⁶ = e^(iπ) = −1. The Prism critical identity, analogous to neg(bnot(x)) = succ(x) in the foundation.",
      "op:lhs": "κ(λ_k(α*(ι(s, ·))), C_shared)",
      "op:rhs": "resolve(s, C_shared)",
      "op:forAll": "s: Literal, C_shared: SharedContext, k: leaseCount",
      "op:verificationDomain": {
        "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/op/PipelineAlgebraic"
      },
      "op:universallyValid": true,
      "op:validityKind": {
        "@id": "https://uor.foundation/op/Universal"
      },
      "op:verificationPathNote": "PI_3 (inference monotonicity) + PA_1 (accumulation associativity) + PL_3 (lease completeness recovery) + PK_2 (composition O(1)) → pipeline equivalence"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://prism.uor.foundation/proof/prf_PI_1",
